rComments: Found I had to teach myself the course. Not very clear at all. Would not recommend taking a class with her. She was willing to meet outside class to explain things which was good, but it would be better if she had just been more clear from the start.

French as a 2nd language grammar class - goes on and on about different kinds of words. Pretty boring, but a lot of material. Worksheets galore. Makes you choose a partner a few days in for ALL projects and doesn't care if you don't get along or if one person doesn't do any work.
